    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable, no-frills ride that gets you from A to B without breaking the bank? This fair-condition vehicle is a practical choice for budget-conscious drivers! It runs and drives reliably for everyday use, though it does show its age with some cosmetic wear and minor imperfections you'd expect at this price point. If you're after dependable transportation at a great value, this one's worth a look!",
      "price": 16500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
